---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Srujan M Padmashali | Profile">
  <header class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-10">
    <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Profile Image" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full grayscale border-2 border-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-100 object-cover shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(24,24,27,0.18)] dark:hover:shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]" />
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Srujan M Padmashali</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mt-1">Software Developer</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2 text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:srujanmpadmashali@gmail.com" class="hover:underline">Email</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/srujanmp" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/srujanmpadmashali" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold border-b border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700 pb-2 mb-4 uppercase">About</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">
      Hey, I'm Srujan. I build backend systems and tinker with full-stack apps. I'm usually writing Go or Node.js, trying to make things run a little faster and scale a little better. When I'm not debugging microservices or tweaking sockets, I'm probably working on random side quests. Keep it simple, make it work.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold border-b border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700 pb-2 mb-4 uppercase">Education</h2>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">BTech in Information Science and Engineering</h3>
        <span class="text-xs">2023 - 2027</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">NMAM Institute of Technology | CGPA: 9</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>